      • markByParts

        public static <K,​V> java.util.Map<com.walkertest.core.Part<K,​V>,​java.lang.Integer> markByParts​(java.util.Set<com.walkertest.core.Part<K,​V>> parts)
        Marks the given Set of Parts.

        The result of the marking is given as a Map which uses Part as its key and an integer as its value. The integer value is the score obtained for that Part

        Type Parameters:
        K - the type of object to use as the Questions' id
        V - the type of object to use as the Questions' raw data
        Parameters:
        parts - the set of @{code Part}s to be marked
        Returns:
        a map in which the integer values represent the scores obtained for the respective Part
